cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the example run data, please cite it as below."
title: "Synthetic Networked Research Institutes"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Hansen
    given-names: Nat
date-released: "2026-07-20"
repository-code: "https://github.com/nathanielhansen-eng/synthetic-networked-research-institutes"
license: MIT
abstract: >-
  An interactive laboratory for experimental institutional epistemology:
  small research institutes staffed by LLM personas with controlled Big Five
  personality profiles, wired into Zollman-style communication networks, work
  on real open research problems while the app measures the diversity and
  correctness of what the network concludes.
keywords:
  - epistemic networks
  - multi-agent simulation
  - experimental philosophy
  - social epistemology
  - large language models
